/uploads/2020/05/hassantrip-150x150.jpg"></a></div></figure><div class="summary"><header><p class="timestamp"><time datetime="2020-05-21T04:53:11+02:00">5/21/20, 4:53 AM CEST</time></p><h4><a href="https://www.politico.eu/interactive/in-pictures-nhs-workers-fighting-to-keep-a-covid-19-ward-safe/">In pictures: NHS workers fighting to keep a COVID-19 ward safe</a></h4></header><footer class="meta"><p class="byline">BY <span class="vcard"><a  class="url fn" href="https://www.politico.eu/author/tim-ball/">Tim Ball</a></span></p></footer><div class="tease"><p>So many of the doctors, nurses, cleaners and other key workers at London&#8217;s Whipps Cross hospital hail from far beyond the UK&#8217;s shores.</p></div></div><!-- ./tease --></article></div><div class="micro-carousel-item already-seen" data-postid="1370244"><article class="timeline-frag"><figure class="thumb"><div class="fig-graphic"><a href="https://www.politico.eu/article/white-house-weighs-shorter-extension-of-nuclear-arms-pact-with-russia/"><img data-lazy="https://www.politico.eu/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GettyImages-472751856-150x150.jpg"></a></div></figure><div class="summary"><header><p class="timestamp"><time datetime="2020-05-21T01:36:36+02:00">5/21/20, 1:36 AM CEST</time></p><h4><a href="https://www.politico.eu/article/white-house-weighs-shorter-extension-of-nuclear-arms-pact-with-russia/">White House weighs shorter extension of nuclear arms pact with Russia</a></h4></header><footer class="meta"><p class="byline">BY <span class="vcard"><a  class="url fn" href="https://www.politico.eu/author/bryan-bender/">Bryan Bender</a></span></p></footer><div class="tease"><p>The option is part of a strategy that would also seek a broader agreement with Moscow that possibly includes China.</p></div></div><!-- ./tease --></article></div><div class="micro-carousel-item already-seen" data-postid="1369155"><article class="timeline-frag"><figure class="thumb"><div class="fig-graphic"><a href="https://www.politico.eu/article/most-americans-say-germans-tackled-coronavirus-better-than-us-report/"><img data-lazy="https://www.politico.eu/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GettyImages-1225045154-150x150.jpg"></a></div></figure><div class="summary"><header><p class="timestamp"><time datetime="2020-05-20T16:00:47+02:00">5/20/20, 4:00 PM CEST</time></p><h4><a href="https://www.politico.eu/article/most-americans-say-germans-tackled-coronavirus-better-than-us-report/">Most Americans say Germans tackled coronavirus better than US: report</a></h4></header><footer class="meta"><p class="byline">BY <span class="vcard"><a  class="url fn" href="https://www.politico.eu/author/laurenz-gehrke/">Laurenz Gehrke</a></span></p></footer><div class="tease"><p>While 66 percent said Berlin responded well to pandemic, 47 percent said the same of Washington.</p></div></div><!-- ./tease --></article></div><div class="micro-carousel-item already-seen" data-postid="1369419"><article class="timeline-frag"><figure class="thumb"><div class="fig-graphic"><a href="https://www.politico.eu/article/coronavirus-the-reason-donald-trump-will-take-a-pill-but-not-advice/"><img data-lazy="https://www.politico.eu/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GettyImages-1214038154-150x150.jpg"></a></div></figure><div class="summary"><header><p class="timestamp"><time datetime="2020-05-20T12:43:59+02:00">5/20/20, 12:43 PM CEST</time></p><h4><a href="https://www.politico.eu/article/coronavirus-the-reason-donald-trump-will-take-a-pill-but-not-advice/">The reason Donald Trump will take a pill but not advice</a></h4></header><footer class="meta"><p class="byline">BY <span class="vcard"><a  class="url fn" href="https://www.politico.eu/author/michael-kruse/">Michael Kruse</a></span></p></footer><div class="tease"><p>He has often paid the price for ignoring experts. But he can also turn it into personal victories.</p></div></div><!-- ./tease --></article></div></div></section></div></li><li class="micro-search subnav format-m pos-beta"><a class="subnav-toggle" h